SELECT Theme, Ticket_Price FROM exhibition WHERE  Year > Year GROUP BY Ticket_Price

SELECT b.Theme FROM exhibition AS b WHERE  b.Exhibition_ID < b.Year LIMIT 7

SELECT artist.Artist_ID AS Artist_ID_x, Year_Join, Ticket_Price FROM exhibition_record JOIN exhibition JOIN artist ON exhibition.Artist_ID = artist.Artist_ID AND exhibition_record.Exhibition_ID = exhibition.Exhibition_ID WHERE Ticket_Price IN (SELECT Ticket_Price FROM exhibition WHERE  Year <> Exhibition_ID) GROUP BY Ticket_Price HAVING MIN(Year) < 86 ORDER BY Artist_ID_x ASC

SELECT o.Ticket_Price, y.Ticket_Price, y.Theme FROM exhibition JOIN exhibition AS y JOIN exhibition AS o ON exhibition.Exhibition_ID = y.Exhibition_ID AND y.Exhibition_ID = o.Exhibition_ID ORDER BY y.Ticket_Price ASC

SELECT Theme, y.Year_Join FROM exhibition JOIN artist JOIN artist AS y ON exhibition.Artist_ID = artist.Artist_ID AND artist.Artist_ID = y.Artist_ID WHERE (Ticket_Price BETWEEN 1 AND 10) AND ( Exhibition_ID >= artist.Artist_ID) GROUP BY y.Year_Join HAVING AVG(exhibition.Artist_ID) = 91 ORDER BY y.Year_Join DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT exhibition_record.Exhibition_ID FROM exhibition_record JOIN exhibition ON exhibition_record.Exhibition_ID = exhibition.Exhibition_ID WHERE (exhibition_record.Exhibition_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10) AND ( exhibition.Exhibition_ID <= Year) ORDER BY exhibition_record.Exhibition_ID ASC
